{"word":"μέμψις","slug":"μέμψις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μέμψις</b></el> <el>(μέμψις, εως,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέμφομαι'><el>μέμφομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>blame, censure, reproof</i>, <el>μ. ἐπιφέρειν τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>ἔχειν μ.</el> to incur <i>blame</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>cause for complaint</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}